      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Daniel Uranga</b>\n</p><p><b>Daniel Uranga</b>,<br />\nan Argentinian engineer and computer chess programmer.\nHe is author of the chess engine <a href=\"/index.php?title=RataAeroespacial&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"RataAeroespacial (page does not exist)\">RataAeroespacial</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>, \nand more recently contributed to <a href=\"/Leela_Chess_Zero\" title=\"Leela Chess Zero\">Leela Chess Zero</a>. He made numerous changes to both the binary and the training code \nand helped <a href=\"/Albert_Silver\" title=\"Albert Silver\">Albert Silver</a> with his efforts leading to <a href=\"/Fat_Fritz\" title=\"Fat Fritz\">Fat Fritz</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Daniel_Uranga&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=4&amp;t=50094\">Help with new chess engine</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel Uranga</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, April 14, 2009</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=22&amp;t=50140\">How to use windows engines in linux with xboard</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel Uranga</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, May 07, 2009</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=4&amp;t=50635\">0x88 FRC castle questions</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel Uranga</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, December 12, 2009&#160;» <a href=\"/0x88\" title=\"0x88\">0x88</a>, <a href=\"/Chess960\" title=\"Chess960\">Chess960</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=4&amp;t=50654\">Small qsearch idea</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel Uranga</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, December 19, 2009</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=19&amp;t=5127\">Question about Xboard, Zippy and Freechess.org</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel Uranga</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, October 27, 2010</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=4&amp;t=51322\">Typhoon chess engine bug &amp; bugfix</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel Uranga</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, November 18, 2010&#160;» <a href=\"/Typhoon\" title=\"Typhoon\">Typhoon</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Daniel_Uranga&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/DanielUranga\">DanielUranga (Daniel Uranga) · GitHub</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://twitter.com/DanielUranga\">Daniel Uranga (@DanielUranga) / Twitter</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Daniel_Uranga&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://ccrl.chessdom.com/ccrl/4040/cgi/engine_details.cgi?print=Details&amp;each_game=1&amp;eng=RataAeroespacial%200.2.1\">RataAeroespacial 0.2.1 in CCRL 40/15</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://sites.google.com/site/rataaeroespacial/\">RataAeroespacial</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.chessbase.com/post/standing-on-the-shoulders-of-giants\">Standing on the shoulders of giants</a> by <a href=\"/Albert_Silver\" title=\"Albert Silver\">Albert Silver</a>, <a href=\"/ChessBase\" title=\"ChessBase\">ChessBase News</a>, September 18, 2019</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/DanielUranga/lc0/tree/uci-wdl-reporting\">GitHub - DanielUranga/lc0 at uci-wdl-reporting</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260228191104\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.007 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.008 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 71/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 162/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:7468-0!canonical and timestamp 20260228191104 and revision id 21563\n -->\n"
